{"tid":1270782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一陣去民陣遊行嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-01T02:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T04:07:24.000Z","uid":247774,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ce951b72485300599bae1a9ce9831fc9b1028555","tid":1270782,"uid":247774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:49:38.000Z","msg":"講真今日唔知會有幾多人，<br />\n（可能唔係重點）<br />\n但點會都多過班廢老藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果去/同家人/朋友去，<br />\n可以嘅夾一夾<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">黑白色衫</span></strong>，<br />\n唔好畀對家話我地拎上次啲相copy and paste，<br />\n呢個時候講dresscode應該會被人鬧我，<br />\n但我只係想避免落人口實。<br />\n（預咗畀大家插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n其實身邊有6.9/6.16遊行嘅人已經飛咗，我因為咁而好嬲佢地，<br />\n覺得佢地打卡講到自己有幾重視，<br />\n但連宜家水深火熱都唔放棄plan，<br />\n去玩完先算，真係好灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連續兩晚接受手足過身好難受，<br />\n喊到豬頭咁。<br />\n<br />\n但大家點都要出席遊行，<br />\n就算係勇武/和理非都好，<br />\n呢個係顯示香港人決心，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家加油！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ad37690de6132abc98f4203d2efdb443dfb06f23","tid":1270782,"uid":247774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:50:25.000Z","msg":"大家努力啦呀！"},{"pid":"47d0e934340b9abc58cd718d1c03687fe0e5f4f1","tid":1270782,"uid":247774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:51:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67297785b870e31722b82e05eda2a02592028181","tid":1270782,"uid":247774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:52:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea3803c32135ed1a802659d662ba99efb21b8761","tid":1270782,"uid":247774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:53:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f33b3014f5c1a006787406853515576c81245266","tid":1270782,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:55:39.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"94b